cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a new approach to improve GAN for image synthesis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces an autoencoder into the categorical discriminator, which involves deep learning techniques (cs.AI). The paper discusses the generation of realistic artworks, which could be related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
